# VisionChain Environment Configuration

# =============================================================================
# CARDANO BLOCKCHAIN (Required for VisionChain features)
# =============================================================================

# Blockfrost API Key for Cardano Preprod Testnet
# Get your free API key from: https://blockfrost.io/
# 1. Sign up at blockfrost.io
# 2. Create a new project
# 3. Select "Cardano Preprod" network
# 4. Copy your project ID here
BLOCKFROST_PROJECT_ID=preprodYourProjectIdHere

# =============================================================================
# SUPABASE DATABASE (Optional - for persistence)
# =============================================================================

# Supabase Project URL
# Get from: https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/_/settings/api
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co

# Supabase Service Role Key (Secret!)
# Get from: https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/_/settings/api
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key-here

# =============================================================================
# GROQ AI (Optional - for chat features)
# =============================================================================

# Groq API Key for AI Chat
# Get your free API key from: https://console.groq.com/keys
GROQ_API_KEY=your-groq-api-key-here

# =============================================================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# =============================================================================

# 1. Copy this file to .env:
#    cp .env.example .env

# 2. Get Blockfrost API Key (REQUIRED for blockchain features):
#    - Go to https://blockfrost.io/
#    - Sign up for free account
#    - Create new project for "Cardano Preprod"
#    - Copy project ID to BLOCKFROST_PROJECT_ID above

# 3. Get testnet ADA (REQUIRED for transactions):
#    - Install Nami or Eternl wallet
#    - Switch to Preprod testnet
#    - Get free test ADA from: https://docs.cardano.org/cardano-testnet/tools/faucet/

# 4. Optional: Set up Supabase for data persistence
#    - Go to https://supabase.com/
#    - Create new project
#    - Copy URL and service role key

# 5. Optional: Set up Groq for AI chat
#    - Go to https://console.groq.com/
#    - Create API key
#    - Copy to GROQ_API_KEY

# =============================================================================
# NOTES
# =============================================================================

# - Never commit the .env file to git (it's in .gitignore)
# - Keep your API keys secret
# - For production, use environment variables instead of .env file
# - Preprod testnet is free - no real ADA required
